# Converters

This folder contains various unit conversion classes and geometric calculation classes for the JSPTH library.
Converters:
1. UnitConvertor
2. TemperatureConvertor
3. TimeConvertor
4. DataStorageConvertor
5. SpeedConvertor
6. PressureConvertor
7. EnergyConvertor
8. VolumeConvertor
9. AngleConvertor
10. FrequencyConvertor
11. CubicConvertor
12. LightConvertor
13. SoundConvertor
14. DataRateConvertor
15. ForceConvertor
16. MagneticFieldConvertor
17. RadiationConvertor
18. DataDensityConvertor
19. AreaConvertor
20. LengthConvertor
21. WeightConvertor
22. WorkConvertor
23. PowerConvertor
24. MiscConvert
25. GeometryConvert
26. ResolutionConvert
27. HerzConvert
28. LuminanceConvert
29. IlluminanceConvert
30. AbsorbedDoseConvert
31. DoseEquivalentConvert
32. CatalyticActivityConvert
33. RadioactivityConvert
34. DensityConvertor
35. WavelengthConvertor
36. ElectricChargeConvertor
37. YieldConvertor
38. MassConvertor
39. areaOfFigures
40. volumeOfFigures
41. areaOf3DFigures
42. perimeterOfFigures
43. perimeterOf3DFigures
44. diagonalOfFigures
45. angleOfFigures
